---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | Mayan K Wellness" headerTheme="light">

    <style>
        .privacy-ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin: 0 0 16px 0;
        }
        .privacy-ul li {
            font-size: 14.5px;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: #55524d;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
    </style>

    <!-- MAIN LAYOUT -->
    <main style="width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: center; padding: 160px 24px 100px 24px; box-sizing: border-box;">
        
        <!-- Privacy Content Container -->
        <div style="background-color: #f4ebd9; border-radius: 16px; padding: 72px 80px; width: 100%; max-width: 820px; box-sizing: border-box;">
            
            <h1 style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 48px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
                Privacy Policy
            </h1>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Introduction</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;">Your privacy matters to me. This policy explains what information I collect when you visit this website or use my coaching services, how I use it, and what rights you have over it.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">This website is operated by [Your Name], trading as [Your Business Name]. If you have any questions about this policy, you can reach me at [your@email.com].</p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">What I collect</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;"><strong>When you visit the website:</strong> I use basic analytics to understand how people find and use the site. This may include your IP address, browser type, which pages you visit, and how long you spend on the site.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;"><strong>When you book a session:</strong> If you book a discovery call or coaching session, I collect the information you provide through the booking form: your name, email address, and any details you share.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;"><strong>When you fill out the contact form:</strong> I collect your name, email address, and the content of your message.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;"><strong>When you subscribe to the newsletter:</strong> I collect your email address and first name.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;"><strong>During coaching sessions:</strong> I may take internal notes to help me track your progress and refer back to past sessions. These notes are kept confidential.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">How I use your information</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">I use the information I collect to:</p>
                <ul class="privacy-ul">
                    <li>Respond to your inquiries and booking requests</li>
                    <li>Deliver coaching services and track your progress</li>
                    <li>Send you emails you've opted into (newsletters, session reminders)</li>
                    <li>Improve the website and understand how visitors use it</li>
                    <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
                </ul>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">I do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Third-party services</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">This website uses the following third-party services that may process your data:</p>
                <ul class="privacy-ul">
                    <li><strong>[Analytics provider]</strong> for website analytics.</li>
                    <li><strong>[Booking platform]</strong> for scheduling sessions.</li>
                    <li><strong>[Email provider]</strong> for sending newsletters and communications.</li>
                    <li><strong>[Payment processor]</strong> for processing payments.</li>
                </ul>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">Each of these services has their own privacy policy governing how they handle your data.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Data retention</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">I keep your personal information only for as long as I need it. Specifically:</p>
                <ul class="privacy-ul">
                    <li><strong>Contact form messages:</strong> 12 months</li>
                    <li><strong>Coaching session notes:</strong> Duration of our working relationship plus 12 months</li>
                    <li><strong>Newsletter subscriber data:</strong> Until you unsubscribe</li>
                    <li><strong>Website analytics data:</strong> 26 months</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Your rights</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">Depending on where you live, you may have the right to:</p>
                <ul class="privacy-ul">
                    <li>Access the personal information I hold about you</li>
                    <li>Correct any inaccurate information</li>
                    <li>Request deletion of your information</li>
                    <li>Withdraw consent for marketing communications at any time</li>
                    <li>Request a copy of your data in a portable format</li>
                </ul>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">To exercise any of these rights, email me at [your@email.com]. I will respond within 30 days.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Children's privacy</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">This website and my coaching services are not directed at children under the age of 18. I do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Changes to this policy</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">I may update this policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Contact</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">If you have any questions about this privacy policy, contact me at [your@email.com].</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>

</BaseLayout>
